{"tid":104926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【嬲嬲豬】澳洲餐廳遭負皮 女店主鬧爆黃絲拒接港客","createTime":"2017-02-02T13:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T09:43:10.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bce8ee8cbaac05cea5e8d7e9454be009234e3948","tid":104926,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:26:01.000Z","msg":"澳洲珀斯一間日式自助餐廳，近日並非因贊助那英《那世界》巡迴演唱會導致「聲名大噪」，而是由於餐廳女店主宣稱不接待香港和內地食客，更挑釁指「黃色絲帶是港獨佔中的標誌」。事件遭到網民非議，在facebook和微信朋友圈議論紛紛，並有網民在fb以港人和內地身份訂位「洗版」。<br />\n<br />\n事源去年12月，來自香港的Jackie到該餐廳用餐，由於餐廳食物味道欠佳，Jackie將用餐意見和建議在該餐廳的fb專頁上發表，並希望餐廳作出改善。之後，有網民寫到：「餐廳景觀好但食物質素差，生蠔不太新鮮，而刺身看起來是一日前的貨色，一點味道也沒有，以75澳元(約440港元)價格有點昂貴，肯定不會再次光顧。」<br />\n<br />\n餐廳fb專頁的留言引起女店主不滿，宣稱以後都不願意接待香港和中國大陸客人，還指香港客人太過挑剔。該女店主在微信朋友圈寫道：「好煩啊，我們還是想主打老外市場，華人只有17萬，老外是200萬啊。」「我真是不願意在朋友圈發這些牢騷的，但是我真的忍不了，來到珀斯也要被這群xx港獨攻擊，真是繞地球一圈來找事，港獨真是超級無聊，沒有共產黨香港只會淪落得更快！」<br />\n<br />\n該日式自助餐廳已將大部份留言刪除，根據fb紀錄顯示，周一有自稱「中華人民共和國香港特別行政區香港永久性居民」的食客查問可否2月5日訂位，該餐廳以英語回覆，餐廳觀迎任何國家和宗教人士入座，餐廳的團隊來自香港、日本、中國、緬甸、西班牙、愛爾蘭、意大利、美國、新加坡、英國、馬來西亞、巴西，以及他作為餐廳總經理則是英國和澳洲的雙國籍人士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170202&amp;guid=56250669&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170202%26guid%3D56250669%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=2edb56a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170202%26guid%3D56250669%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=1fafaa86\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170202&amp;guid=56250669&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"2bf17ef419ec3c6431a10aa24f72eb79efacf5fb","tid":104926,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:36:39.000Z","msg":"屌做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2786ecb20990e12a9767eea60383661de0231c52","tid":104926,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:40:19.000Z","msg":"一定係佔中阻街搞到d海鮮送唔切唔新鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f135d4c26e9720757697fb60d7e47a4a94a8457","tid":104926,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:43:59.000Z","msg":"咁愛國點解做日式自助餐，應該做自助雞煲"},{"pid":"e197d430a3277ab9acd63a08bf960c4f26bc3b0f","tid":104926,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:44:02.000Z","msg":"屌你澳洲人，人哋港獨定旺角自己獨都唔關你事啦"},{"pid":"7ec904a5bda652ecf706dcac1b68cd7e2bbb06cd","tid":104926,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"黃絲帶同港獨係兩樣野嚟架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23f1eef3ad93dc2834a98f94f78bdd05a2043d4","tid":104926,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃絲帶同港獨係兩樣野嚟架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又有幾多人識分<br />\n無知真係可怕"},{"pid":"81a913552df78f31c6add852ce2f2a52b85d186c","tid":104926,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:30:05.000Z","msg":"女店主明顯係大陸蝗啦"},{"pid":"b44da3415af2d662d48cf3569eddba1d7d7e120a","tid":104926,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:34:22.000Z","msg":"講食物咪講食物，又扯左去政治"},{"pid":"e4f654b6cf8910115a4f1c72b43e41d386e202c8","tid":104926,"uid":43173